  "about": {
    "title": "About me",
    "intro": "To be completed in Phase 4.",
    "details": "To be completed in Phase 4.",
    "paragraphs": {
      "1": "I'm Tanguy Delrieu, a BIM specialist trained at the École Spéciale des Travaux Publics de Paris (ESTP). Originally from Nouméa, I specialize in coordinating and modeling digital building models — from structural works through to commissioning.",
      "2": "I've coordinated BIM models at Vinci Construction in Geneva — as-built capture with the HoloLens 2 and BCF tracking on BimCollab — and run site supervision on structural and renovation projects in New Caledonia. I work with Revit, Navisworks and NEXT-BIM, and I'm drawn to everything that brings the digital model closer to the field."
    }
